flowchart TD
    subgraph Human["Human (Owner)"]
        Q[Ask a question OR click 'Build today's plan']
        Review[Reviews AI answer + confidence + citations]
    end

    subgraph Deterministic["Deterministic Core (unchanged, always trusted)"]
        Sched[Scheduler: prioritize / assign slots / detect_conflicts]
    end

    subgraph AI["AI Care Advisor"]
        Retriever[Retriever: TF-IDF DocStore over knowledge/*.md]
        Agent[Agent: Claude + citation-required prompt]
        Evaluator[Evaluator / Guardrails: scope check -> grounding check -> confidence score]
        Logger[(Interaction Log: logs/interactions.jsonl)]
    end

    Q -->|question text| Retriever
    Q -->|generated plan| Sched
    Sched -->|plan + rule-based conflicts| Agent
    Retriever -->|top-k cited chunks| Agent
    Agent -->|draft answer w/ citations| Evaluator

    Evaluator -->|scope refusal: redirect to vet| Review
    Evaluator -->|ungrounded: reject/flag low confidence| Review
    Evaluator -->|grounded: answer + confidence + sources| Review
    Evaluator --> Logger

    Sched -->|rule-based conflicts, always shown separately| Review

    subgraph Testing["Offline Testing (pytest, no network)"]
        T1[test_retrieval.py: correct doc retrieved]
        T2[test_guardrails.py: catches fake citations, flags emergencies]
        T3[test_advisor.py: stub client checks prompt + parsing + logging]
    end

    Retriever -.verified by.-> T1
    Evaluator -.verified by.-> T2
    Agent -.verified by.-> T3
